* Prize, Kraków Medical Academy, 1922 <ref name="Anigstein">{{cite journal|last1=Anigstein|first1=Ludwig|title=Helene Sparrow-Germa, M. D. (1891 - 1970) A Pioneer in World Health|journal=Polish Medical Science and History Bulletin|date=1971|volume=14|issue=3|pages=100–101|accessdate=12 June 2014}}</ref>
